// --- Annotations ---
annotation 1 [[0.80, 0.85]] Globally commoditised: fiat rails, mobile, compute, copper, fossil energy
annotation 2 [[0.35, 0.20]] Local constraints still dominate: identity, trust, mesh, minigrids, CBDC
annotation 3 [[0.55, 0.50]] Evolution battleground: crypto/CBDC/consensus squeeze traditional banking rails
